    <string name="style_realistic">Photorealistic</string>
    <string name="style_realistic_desc">Crystal-clear Google Street View quality. Perfect lighting, sharp details, exactly what you\'d see walking down the street on a pleasant day.</string>

    <string name="style_cinematic">Cinematic Golden Hour</string>
    <string name="style_cinematic_desc">Hollywood magic hour vibes. Warm amber sunlight, long dramatic shadows, lens flares dancing through the scene. Every frame is movie-poster worthy.</string>

    <string name="style_rainy">Moody Rainy Day</string>
    <string name="style_rainy_desc">Wet streets glistening with reflections, misty atmosphere, neon signs bleeding color into puddles. That cozy \"watching rain from a cafe\" aesthetic.</string>

    <string name="style_vintage">Retro Throwback</string>
    <string name="style_vintage_desc">Step into a time machine! Faded colors, film grain, slight vignette - like a Polaroid from the \'70s your parents might have taken.</string>

    <string name="style_anime">Anime World</string>
    <string name="style_anime_desc">Your neighborhood reimagined by Studio Ghibli. Vibrant colors, dreamy skies with fluffy clouds, that magical Japanese animation style that makes everything feel alive.</string>

